Woo.

789
00:59:46,520 --> 00:59:47,920
I'm going back to school now.

790
01:00:10,880 --> 01:00:12,160
Done, Sipakorn.

791
01:00:12,160 --> 01:00:12,800
Ha.

792
01:00:13,840 --> 01:00:14,920
Thank you.

793
01:00:18,600 --> 01:00:19,320
Sigh.

794
01:00:20,560 --> 01:00:21,320
Hehe.

795
01:00:22,080 --> 01:00:24,880
Welcome back.

796
01:00:25,880 --> 01:00:27,800
Jeez, what's wrong with you guys?

797
01:00:28,360 --> 01:00:29,360
You're embarrassing me.

798
01:00:29,360 --> 01:00:32,000
Wow, looking cool
on your first day back.

799
01:00:32,000 --> 01:00:33,440
Hmm.

800
01:00:33,600 --> 01:00:35,640
You didn't reply
in our Line chat at all.

801
01:00:35,640 --> 01:00:37,000
- True.
- You make me think you're a freshman.

802
01:00:37,160 --> 01:00:38,240
Started with friends,
graduating with the juniors.

803
01:00:38,600 --> 01:00:39,520
Aren't you embarrassed, bro?

804
01:00:39,520 --> 01:00:41,280
Hey, what's there to be
embarrassed about, First?

805
01:00:41,280 --> 01:00:42,320
Let me tell you something.

806
01:00:42,480 --> 01:00:46,160
- I'll graduate with a better GPA than you.
- Wow.

807
01:00:46,240 --> 01:00:47,760
- So boastful.
- Ow.

808
01:00:47,760 --> 01:00:48,880
- Ow, let go.
- Come on.

809
01:00:48,880 --> 01:00:49,920
Come on.

810
01:00:49,920 --> 01:00:51,360
- Come on, let's go.
- Woo-hoo.

811
01:00:51,360 --> 01:00:52,480
- Easy, Wayu.
- Sigh.

812
01:00:52,480 --> 01:00:53,280
Can I have a hug?

813
01:00:53,280 --> 01:00:54,560
- Come on.
- There, there.

814
01:00:59,680 --> 01:01:00,320
Sigh.

815
01:01:00,800 --> 01:01:02,000
Wayu's only been gone a day,

816
01:01:02,240 --> 01:01:03,680
and it already feels so lonely.

817
01:01:03,880 --> 01:01:04,640
Sigh.

818
01:01:05,560 --> 01:01:07,040
Emm.

819
01:01:07,400 --> 01:01:08,920
Is he really coming today?

820
01:01:10,080 --> 01:01:10,880
I know.

821
01:01:10,960 --> 01:01:12,600
It's lonely when Sky's not around too.

822
01:01:13,880 --> 01:01:14,400
Sigh.

823
01:01:15,600 --> 01:01:17,280
It feels weirdly empty, doesn't it?

824
01:01:18,600 --> 01:01:19,160
But

825
01:01:19,680 --> 01:01:20,800
he's doing big things now.

826
01:01:21,040 --> 01:01:22,160
So we should be happy, right?

827
01:01:23,520 --> 01:01:24,640
So, who's been missing

828
01:01:24,640 --> 01:01:26,800
- me?
- Whoa.

829
01:01:26,800 --> 01:01:28,160
Student Wayu

830
01:01:28,160 --> 01:01:30,560
is here now.

831
01:01:30,560 --> 01:01:35,480
- It's me, buddy.
- There, there.

832
01:01:36,920 --> 01:01:38,920
I literally just reported
for my first day.

833
01:01:38,920 --> 01:01:40,360
It hasn't even been 24 hours yet.

834
01:01:40,600 --> 01:01:42,160
You're exaggerating, Tai.

835
01:01:42,640 --> 01:01:43,640
I miss you, you know.

836
01:01:44,280 --> 01:01:50,400
- Miss you.
- Geez.

837
01:01:50,400 --> 01:01:51,440
Hmm.

838
01:01:51,680 --> 01:01:53,480
Honestly, the student uniform

839
01:01:54,200 --> 01:01:56,120
does make you look a lot more expensive.

840
01:01:57,040 --> 01:01:57,880
What a waste.

841
01:01:58,160 --> 01:01:59,800
My place has standards.

842
01:02:00,560 --> 01:02:02,360
Still, our bar's already got cops,

843
01:02:02,480 --> 01:02:05,240
doctors, nurses,
and firefighters covered.

844
01:02:05,760 --> 01:02:06,880
Mind your own business.

845
01:02:07,160 --> 01:02:07,680
Ow.

846
01:02:08,080 --> 01:02:09,080
Hey, you guys.

847
01:02:09,400 --> 01:02:10,640
If you're going to give him
something, just give it.

848
01:02:10,840 --> 01:02:12,080
Stop putting on a show.

849
01:02:13,760 --> 01:02:16,240
Tada-da-daaa!

850
01:02:16,520 --> 01:02:19,600
- Tada-da-daaa!
- Tada-da-daaa!

851
01:02:19,840 --> 01:02:20,360
Here you go.

852
01:02:21,040 --> 01:02:23,280
We all chipped in to get this for you.

853
01:02:23,280 --> 01:02:24,120
For school.

854
01:02:24,360 --> 01:02:26,680
So you won't have to
bleed yourself dry to buy one.

855
01:02:27,000 --> 01:02:28,080
This is from all of us.

856
01:02:28,160 --> 01:02:29,120
But the specs,

857
01:02:29,520 --> 01:02:30,560
I picked them myself.

858
01:02:31,840 --> 01:02:32,800
- Check it out. Pretty great, right?
- Oh, wow.

859
01:02:32,800 --> 01:02:35,800
Wow.

860
01:02:35,800 --> 01:02:37,080
Let me see.

861
01:02:37,840 --> 01:02:40,320
If you picked it,
I'd better check first.

862
01:02:40,320 --> 01:02:41,080
Darn.

863
01:02:41,080 --> 01:02:42,200
You're totally not trustworthy.

864
01:02:42,240 --> 01:02:44,080
Darn, I shouldn't have picked it.

865
01:02:44,440 --> 01:02:47,200
Just kidding.

866
01:02:47,280 --> 01:02:49,200
Thanks.

867
01:02:49,320 --> 01:02:49,960
Wayu.

868
01:02:50,280 --> 01:02:50,960
Yeah?

869
01:02:51,200 --> 01:02:52,400
You can come back anytime.

870
01:02:52,800 --> 01:02:53,800
You're welcome anytime.

871
01:02:54,120 --> 01:02:55,480
Feel free to perform anytime.

872
01:02:56,080 --> 01:02:57,120
I've kept the outfits for you.

873
01:02:57,320 --> 01:02:58,200
Alright.

874
01:02:58,240 --> 01:02:59,640
In that case, when I'm free,

875
01:02:59,640 --> 01:03:01,160
I'll entertain everyone
so they're not lonely.

876
01:03:02,680 --> 01:03:03,520
Don't worry, Foei.

877
01:03:04,200 --> 01:03:05,280
Yeah. Good.

878
01:03:05,720 --> 01:03:06,280
Oh.

879
01:03:06,640 --> 01:03:08,320
- Hmm.
- Oh!

880
01:03:08,560 --> 01:03:09,400
And you guys,

881
01:03:09,640 --> 01:03:11,080
aren't you going to
prepare for the show?

882
01:03:11,360 --> 01:03:12,480
What time is it?

883
01:03:13,360 --> 01:03:14,080
Go.

884
01:03:14,440 --> 01:03:15,040
Wayu.

885
01:03:15,360 --> 01:03:16,760
Why not hang out together today?

886
01:03:17,040 --> 01:03:18,200
I'll treat you.

887
01:03:19,800 --> 01:03:20,400
Sure.

888
01:03:20,560 --> 01:03:22,960
Then I'm going to
eat my fill. Consider it

889
01:03:23,120 --> 01:03:24,200
a send-off meal.

890
01:03:24,360 --> 01:03:25,760
- Yeah, good.
- Good.

891
01:03:25,880 --> 01:03:27,240
- Go.
- Change clothes.

892
01:03:27,360 --> 01:03:28,840
Alright, go.

893
01:03:29,040 --> 01:03:30,400
Sigh.

894
01:03:30,400 --> 01:03:32,560
- Line up and go "Whoa."
- If Wayu doesn't come to the bar...

895
01:03:32,760 --> 01:03:33,480
Go.

896
01:03:52,240 --> 01:03:53,160
(New Post)

897
01:03:53,600 --> 01:03:55,000
(POV:)

898
01:03:55,200 --> 01:03:56,160
(Single)

899
01:03:56,280 --> 01:03:58,160
(and ready to mingle.)

900
01:04:13,800 --> 01:04:14,520
I'm back.

901
01:04:16,480 --> 01:04:17,200
Who are you talking to?

902
01:04:29,760 --> 01:04:31,360
(I'm yours alone.)

903
01:04:32,440 --> 01:04:33,880
Hey.

904
01:04:36,000 --> 01:04:36,600
Hmm.

905
01:05:45,080 --> 01:05:46,720
The guy I had watching him said...

906
01:05:48,440 --> 01:05:49,800
The bar announced

907
01:05:49,800 --> 01:05:51,680
that Wayu already quit.

908
01:05:54,880 --> 01:05:55,480
Mm.

909
01:05:59,080 --> 01:06:01,000
Looks like he's really moving on.

910
01:06:02,080 --> 01:06:03,800
- As for you...
- It's okay.

911
01:06:06,400 --> 01:06:07,400
Maybe that's for the best.

912
01:06:25,120 --> 01:06:26,880
So you're really selling this condo?

913
01:06:29,760 --> 01:06:30,800
You're not keeping it?

914
01:06:36,720 --> 01:06:37,600
I don't know.

915
01:06:39,800 --> 01:06:41,160
There's no point holding onto it.

916
01:06:44,680 --> 01:06:45,720
I've made up my mind.

917
01:06:46,880 --> 01:06:48,400
I'll have to live with the consequences.

918
01:06:54,200 --> 01:06:56,720
As your friend and supporter,
I'm rooting for you.

919
01:07:02,520 --> 01:07:03,120
Krit.

920
01:07:04,520 --> 01:07:05,280
You know that, right?

921
01:07:07,800 --> 01:07:09,560
You can't go back and undo things now.

922
01:07:20,480 --> 01:07:21,000
I know.

923
01:07:24,640 --> 01:07:26,120
But even so,
I'd still make the same choice.

924
01:07:29,200 --> 01:07:29,760
Sigh.

925
01:08:27,120 --> 01:08:28,480
Now that you're up, come eat with us.

926
01:08:33,840 --> 01:08:35,360
You full? Want more?

927
01:08:35,480 --> 01:08:36,240
Want me to feed you?

928
01:08:37,280 --> 01:08:38,160
You're not eating?

929
01:08:38,720 --> 01:08:39,320
Dip it in the sauce first.

930
01:08:39,520 --> 01:08:40,400
Want some sauce too?

931
